  "text": "This functor coincides with the semi-infinite cohomology group H 1=2+0 (g, M), see Section 1.3, for a class of modules M called semijective in [CITATION_1] Corollary 3.4 ]. We will recall this notion along with a more general concept of a semijective resolution below in Section 1.6.",
